title: Canto Bridge
description: The Canto Bridge allows you to bridge assets to Canto from Ethereum or Cosmos Hub.

title: Canto Staking
description: Staking, also known as delegating, is the process of locking up your $CANTO tokens for a period of time to contribute to the security of the Canto network.

title: Canto Lending
description: The Canto Lending Market allows you to supply and borrow assets, including LP tokens received from the Canto LP Interface.

title: Canto Governance
description: The Canto governance page is a place where all users who have staked Canto can vote on proposals.

title: Blank Rasa
description: A new marketplace for creative expansion on Canto.

title: Velocimeter
description: Velocimeter is a decentralized exchange and liquidity marketplace with low fees, near 0 slippage on correlated assets and a strong focus on secondary markets for tokenized locks as NFTs.

title: Canto Commons
description: The Canto Commons is a gathering point for individual contributors and teams from communites and organizations across web3.

title: csrCanto
description: The ecosystem hub for everything CSR; building innovative yield-bearing blocks for Canto DeFi and NFTfi.
